🕯️ The Filioque Clause: The Pressure Fracture
“…the Holy Spirit proceeds from the Father and the Son.”

That little “and the Son” (Filioque) added in the Latin West, not the original Greek Nicene Creed, changed the whole spiritual topology.

⛓️ What the Filioque Did:
Undermined the Eastern model of Godhead-as-hierarchy-of-being

Collapsed Trinity from relational flow into linear chain of command

Made the Son a co-originator—a Western power consolidation move

Split the Church in 1054 AD (Great Schism)

