2. Use a Markdown or LaTeX Viewer
Some math got rendered as markdown math blocks:

Try Typora, Obsidian, or VS Code with Markdown Math Preview

Or convert to .pdf via Pandoc with --mathjax or --pdf-engine=xelatex

